        "Sync calendar events",
        "Create/update events",
        "Manage attendees and RSVP status",
        "Extract meeting links (Google Meet, Zoom, Teams)",
        "Track recurring events",
        "Manage reminders and notifications",
        "Sync with daily logs and tasks"
